data.description: MAJOR PRICE REDUCTION!!! Spacious 3bd/2ba in desirable Fountain Park. Formal dining at the front of the home, nice open kitchen leads into the large family room with wood burning fireplace. Large main bedroom, separate laundry room and in kitchen breakfast bar. Fantastic home to entertain in with nice backyard & covered patios. Storm shelter for 6, all new plumbing throughout ‘18, new privacy fence, new roof ‘21. Motivated sellers, schedule a tour today!
